Announcing the release of ggz-client-libs-0.0.4!

The GGZ client libraries currently consists of the single library
ggzcore.  ggzcore provide core client functionality for all of the GGZ
client frontends.  It handles services such as client server
communication, game module management, etc.

This is the first public release of the code for ggz-client-libs.  Its
API is still somewhat under development, but the code is used by the
text, gtk, and kde frontends

